lyrics:
[Verse]
In the heart of the forest, where legends are born
Roams a mighty herd, with power untold
Their coats radiant, gleaming bright
The Cheese Reindeer, ready to take flight

[Chorus]
Oh, Cheese Reindeer, of strength and grace
Guiding us through every earthly place
Together we stand, never to fall
The League of Mighty Cheese Reindeer, above all
